OOC: Not her fault, she's from Mexico. At least she tries!

BIC: Blackfang nodded. He knew there was something wrong with the 
Predacon base being attacked, but he couldn't point it out. There were 
those gunshot marks on the Maximal base too... Something had happened 
and he was pretty sure those new guys were the cause.

Blackfang: I am ready to go, but I think we will have to take 
prisoners. Why would someone else be attacking the preds and not 
contact us, because they must know we are here...
